  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >One Minute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the frantic universe of <u><strong>One Minute</strong></u>, a <strong>roguelite</strong> game like no other where every second counts! Designed to be <strong>fast</strong>, <strong>accessible</strong>, and <strong>addictive</strong>, this game offers an intense experience entirely controlled with your mouse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <u><strong>Fast and varied mini-games</strong></u>: Face a series of 12 mini-games, each lasting only 5 seconds. Your goal? Achieve the highest score possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💻 <strong><u>Accessibility and performance</u></strong>: Smooth gameplay even on low-end PCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏋️ <strong><u>Training mode</u></strong>: Perfect your skills on your favorite mini-games. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️ <u><strong>Roguelite progression</strong></u>: Earn money by playing and use it to unlock new mini-games or upgrade the ones you already own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <u><strong>Global leaderboards</strong></u>: Compare your scores with players worldwide, mini-game by mini-game or through an overall leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖱️ <u><strong>Unique cursor skins</strong></u>: Earn rare mouse cursor skins after every game, which can be traded on the Steam Marketplace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an intense and addictive experience where every click counts! 🕒</p>",
